title: Elegear USB C to Lightning Cable [MFi Certified] 3Pack 2M Fast Charging Type C to iPhone Charger Cable Supports Power…
html: Elegear USB C to Lightning Cable [MFi Certified] 3Pack 2M Fast Charging Type C to iPhone Charger Cable Supports Power…
description: ⚡【MFi Certified】Elegear USB C to lightning cable has completed MFi certification requirements. The MFi certification and Elegear strict quality testing ensure the safety of your devices. The high quality copper wire supports fast data transferring up to 480Mbp/s, helping you to transfer files, music, movies, pictures quickly and stably. ⚡【Power Delivery Fast Charging】Charge your iPhone 12 from 0% to 50% in just 30 mins. Elegear type C to lightning cable supports fast charging for iPhone 12, 12 Mini, 12 Pro, 12 Pro Max, 11, 11 Pro, 11 Pro Max, SE, X, XS, XR, XS Max, 8, 8 Plus etc (including 18W, 20W, 29W, 30W, 61W, or 87W USB-C Power Adapter). ⚡【New C94 Connector】This iPhone charger cable uses the Newest C94 lightning end which is specially designed for fast charging, whose color is different from the previous C48 lightning end. Charging Speeds 2.5× Faster than USB A to Lightning Cable. It shorten time to charge and improve your work efficient. You can get your phones charging done in less time.
